      "span_text": "ß-N-acetyl-glucosaminidase (EC 3.2.1.30), ß-D-glucuronidase (EC 3.2.1.31), ß-Nacetyl-galactosaminidase (EC 3.2.1.53) and ß-galactosidase (EC 3.2.1.23) were assayed as previously described by [CITATION_1] using, respectively,"
